# ── Frontend: npm devDependency transitive packages ──────────────────────────
# These CVEs are in devDependencies only (vue-tsc, @vue/test-utils toolchain).
# Not present in production builds. Fix requires major version bumps with
# breaking changes in the test toolchain.

# minimatch <10.2.1 → CVE-2026-26996 (DoS via crafted input)
# Transitive via vue-tsc → @volar/language-core. Requires minimatch 10.x (major bump).
CVE-2026-26996 exp:2026-06-01

# node-tar 6.x → CVE-2026-23745, CVE-2026-23950, CVE-2026-24842, CVE-2026-26960
# Transitive via @vue/test-utils build toolchain. Fix requires tar 7.x (major bump).
CVE-2026-23745 exp:2026-06-01
CVE-2026-23950 exp:2026-06-01
CVE-2026-24842 exp:2026-06-01
CVE-2026-26960 exp:2026-06-01

